{"id":788,"parent_id":769,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":788,"title":"Jeremiah 19","subtitle":"","short_title":"Jer.","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 19"],[".studySummary",["i","The Lord will bring evil upon Judah—They sacrifice their children to Baal—In the siege they will eat the flesh of their sons and daughters."]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.1","order":"02.25.019.52108"},["b","1"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", Go and get a",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"potter’s"],"earthen bottle, and",["i","take"],"of the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_1b"},"ancients"],"of the people, and of the ancients of the priests;"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.2","order":"02.25.019.52109"},["b","2"],"And go forth unto the valley of the son of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_2a"},"Hinnom"],", which",["i","is"],"by the entry of the east gate, and proclaim there the words that I shall tell thee,"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.3","order":"02.25.019.52110"},["b","3"],"And say, Hear ye the word of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", O kings of Judah, and inhabitants of Jerusalem; Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, the God of Israel; Behold, I will bring evil upon this place, the which whosoever heareth, his ears shall",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_3a"},"tingle"],"."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4","order":"02.25.019.52111"},["b","4"],"Because they have",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_4a"},"forsaken"],"me, and have",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_4b"},"estranged"],"this place, and have burned incense in it unto other",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_4c"},"gods"],", whom neither they nor their fathers have known, nor the kings of Judah, and have filled this place with the",["sup","d"],["a",{"href":"fn_4d"},"blood"],"of innocents;"],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.5","order":"02.25.019.52112"},["b","5"],"They have built also the high places of Baal, to burn their sons with",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_5a"},"fire"],["i","for"],"burnt offerings unto Baal, which I commanded not, nor spake",["i","it,"],"neither came",["i","it"],"into my mind:"],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.6","order":"02.25.019.52113"},["b","6"],"Therefore, behold, the days come, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", that this place shall no more be called",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"Tophet"],", nor The valley of the son of Hinnom, but The valley of slaughter."],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.7","order":"02.25.019.52114"},["b","7"],"And I will make void the counsel of Judah and Jerusalem in this place; and I will cause them to fall by the sword before their enemies, and by the hands of them that seek their lives: and their",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"carcases"],"will I give to be meat for the fowls of the heaven, and for the beasts of the earth."],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.8","order":"02.25.019.52115"},["b","8"],"And I will make this city",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"desolate"],", and an hissing; every one that passeth thereby shall be astonished and hiss because of all the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_8b"},"plagues"],"thereof."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9","order":"02.25.019.52116"},["b","9"],"And I will cause them to",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_9a"},"eat"],"the flesh of their sons and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_9b"},"flesh"],"of their daughters, and they shall eat every one the flesh of his friend in the siege and straitness, wherewith their enemies, and they that seek their lives, shall",["sup","c"],["a",{"href":"fn_9c"},"straiten"],"them."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.10","order":"02.25.019.52117"},["b","10"],"Then shalt thou break the bottle in the sight of the men that go with thee,"],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.11","order":"02.25.019.52118"},["b","11"],"And shalt say unto them, Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts; Even so will I break this people and this city, as",["i","one"],"breaketh a potter’s vessel, that cannot be made whole again: and they shall bury",["i","them"],"in Tophet, till",["i","there be"],"no place to bury."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.12","order":"02.25.019.52119"},["b","12"],"Thus will I do unto this place, saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],", and to the inhabitants thereof, and",["i","even"],"make this city as Tophet:"],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.13","order":"02.25.019.52120"},["b","13"],"And the houses of Jerusalem, and the houses of the kings of Judah, shall be defiled as the place of Tophet, because of all the houses upon whose",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_13a"},"roofs"],"they have burned incense unto all the host of heaven, and have poured out drink offerings unto other gods."],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.14","order":"02.25.019.52121"},["b","14"],"Then came Jeremiah from Tophet, whither the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"had sent him to prophesy; and he stood in the court of the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"’s house; and said to all the people,"],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.15","order":"02.25.019.52122"},["b","15"],"Thus saith the",["span.smallCaps","Lord"],"of hosts, the God of Israel; Behold, I will bring upon this city and upon all her towns all the evil that I have pronounced against it, because they have hardened their necks, that they might not hear my words."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.1a","order":"02.25.019.52123"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.2"},"Jer. 18:2"],"."],["div",{"id":"1b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.1b","order":"02.25.019.52125"},["b","1b"],["span.small","OR"],"elders."],["div",{"id":"2a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.2a","order":"02.25.019.52127"},["b","2a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/josh/18.16"},"Josh. 18:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"3a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.3a","order":"02.25.019.52129"},["b","3a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-sam/3.11"},"1 Sam. 3:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/21.12"},"2 Kgs. 21:12"],"."],["div",{"id":"4a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4a","order":"02.25.019.52131"},["b","4a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/1.16"},"Jer. 1:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"4b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4b","order":"02.25.019.52133"},["b","4b"],["span.small","OR"],"alienated."],["div",{"id":"4c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4c","order":"02.25.019.52135"},["b","4c"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/idolatry"},"TG Idolatry"],"."],["div",{"id":"4d","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.4d","order":"02.25.019.52137"},["b","4d"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/2.34.31-37"},"Jer. 2:34 (31–37)"],"."],["div",{"id":"5a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.5a","order":"02.25.019.52139"},["b","5a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/18.21"},"Lev. 18:21"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/32.35"},"Jer. 32:35"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/morm/4.14"},"Morm. 4:14"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.6a","order":"02.25.019.52141"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.10"},"2 Kgs. 23:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.7a","order":"02.25.019.52143"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/7.33"},"Jer. 7:33"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/16.10"},"Alma 16:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.8a","order":"02.25.019.52145"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/jer/18.16"},"Jer. 18:16"],"."],["div",{"id":"8b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.8b","order":"02.25.019.52147"},["b","8b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/plague"},"TG Plague"],"."],["div",{"id":"9a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9a","order":"02.25.019.52149"},["b","9a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lev/26.29"},"Lev. 26:29"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/deut/28.53"},"Deut. 28:53"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/2.20"},"Lam. 2:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ezek/5.10"},"Ezek. 5:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9b","order":"02.25.019.52151"},["b","9b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/isa/9.20"},"Isa. 9:20"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/lam/4.10"},"Lam. 4:10"],"."],["div",{"id":"9c","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.9c","order":"02.25.019.52153"},["b","9c"],["span.small","OR"],"distress or afflict."],["div",{"id":"13a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/jer/19.13a","order":"02.25.019.52155"},["b","13a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/2-kgs/23.12"},"2 Kgs. 23:12"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/zeph/1.5"},"Zeph. 1:5"],"."]]}
